File Structure
Generated code
.
├── accounts/
│   └── your_account_cookies.json  # Indeed account cookies
├── fingerprints/
│   └── your_fingerprint.json      # Browser fingerprint data
├── input/
│   └── processed_jobs.txt         # Stores IDs of scraped jobs to avoid duplicates
├── output/
│   └── jobs.xlsx                  # The final Excel output file
├── utils/
│   ├── bypass/
│   │   └── cloudflare.py          # Cloudflare Turnstile bypass logic
│   ├── __init__.py
│   ├── accounts_loader.py         # Loads Indeed accounts
│   ├── fingerprint_loader.py      # Loads browser fingerprints
│   ├── helper.py                  # Utility functions (AI, simulation, file I/O)
│   ├── proxies_loader.py          # Loads proxies
│   └── sheet_uploader.py          # Handles Excel and Google Sheets operations
├── .env                           # API keys (Groq, 2Captcha)
├── config_input.py                # Main user configuration
├── gs_credentials.json            # Google Sheets API service account key
├── job_details_scraper.py         # Scrapes individual job pages
├── job_listings_scraper.py        # Scrapes job search result pages
├── main.py                        # The main entry point to run the scraper
├── proxies.txt                    # List of proxies
├── requirements.txt               # Python package dependencies
└── scraper_setting.py             # Technical scraper settings
